# Main Functional Requirements

## 1. Authentication

Single admin authentication system.

Requirements:
- login/password auth
- JWT auth
- refresh tokens
- protected admin routes
- logout
- secure password hashing
- middleware authorization

Admin can:
- create content
- edit content
- delete content
- reorder content
- manage homepage collections

---

# Content Models

## Tour

Fields:

```ts
{
  id: string

  title_ru: string
  title_en: string

  description_ru: string
  description_en: string

  country_ru: string
  country_en: string

  city_ru: string
  city_en: string

  agency_ru: string
  agency_en: string

  earnings: string

  contacts: string

  is_vip: boolean
  hidden_vip: boolean

  tags: string[]

  image_url: string

  created_at: Date
}
```

---

## Service

```ts
{
  id: string

  title_ru: string
  title_en: string

  description_ru: string
  description_en: string

  price: string

  contacts: string

  tags: string[]

  image_url: string

  created_at: Date
}
```

---

## Blog Article

```ts
{
  id: string

  title_ru: string
  title_en: string

  content_ru_markdown: string
  content_en_markdown: string

  preview_image: string

  tags: string[]

  hidden_vip: boolean

  created_at: Date
}
```

