# Homepage Architecture

Homepage contains horizontal scrollable sections.

Sections:
- Featured Tours
- Featured Services
- Featured Blog Posts

Each section:
- horizontal card carousel
- swipe support
- mobile optimized
- smooth animation

Admin must be able to:
- manually curate homepage collections
- reorder cards with drag-and-drop
- pin/unpin content

---

# Navigation

Bottom navigation only.

Tabs:
- Home
- Tours
- Blog
- Services
- Contacts

Requirements:
- Telegram-native feeling
- fixed bottom navigation
- smooth transitions
- active state highlighting

---

# Tours / Services / Blog Pages

All three sections share the same architecture.

Requirements:
- searchable card list
- filters modal
- tag-based filtering
- infinite scroll or pagination
- responsive cards
- premium dark appearance

Each card:
- image
- title
- short description
- tags
- VIP indicator if needed

---

# Markdown Blog System

Requirements:
- markdown editor
- live preview
- image embedding support
- markdown rendering
- syntax highlighting
- responsive typography

Use:
- react-markdown
- remark-gfm
- rehype-highlight

---

# Image Upload System

Requirements:
- drag and drop uploader
- image compression
- progress indicator
- Supabase Storage integration
- image preview
- validation

Supported:
- jpg
- png
- webp

Use:
- browser-image-compression

---

# VIP Content System

Implement hidden VIP content logic.

Requirements:
- hidden VIP entries
- conditional rendering
- VIP badges
- protected visibility logic

Architecture must allow future extension:
- paid subscriptions
- Telegram premium access
- invite-only access

---

# Contacts System

Requirements:
- Telegram username links
- clickable buttons
- Telegram deep links
- external social/contact support

---

# Internationalization

Languages:
- Russian
- English

Requirements:
- manual translations
- field-level translations
- language switcher
- persistent selected language

Use:
- i18next

